&lt;p>Apache Hive is a data warehousing and SQL-like query engine built on top of Hadoop. It provides a platform for processing large datasets stored in Hadoop Distributed File System (HDFS) and other data storage systems that integrate with Hadoop. Hive simplifies querying and managing big data with a familiar SQL-like syntax (HiveQL). Below are the key capabilities of Hive:&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>